{"tid":2227113,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何依婷慘登色情網變「小仙女Baby」　三圍數字竟遭竄改","createTime":"2020-10-02T13:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T13:57:56.000Z","uid":244704,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"db5489bf6c95f14d7a45e88c2120b6ee3bfb7453","tid":2227113,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T13:46:13.000Z","msg":"　　2017年港姐亞軍何依婷（Regina）一卸任就備受力捧，由《學是學非》是非精到近來擔任幾個大型節目主持，加上喺劇集《機場特警》中飾演港女網紅李至安，坐喺戲中男友楊明大腿上一幕引起熱議。估唔到最近更被色情網站偷相，指何依婷可以提供「絲襪制服誘惑」﹗<br />\n<br />\n　　色情網以「小仙女BABY」之名，放上四張何依婷嘅相片，身穿短袖LACE上衣配窄身短裙，一貫Regina出活動衣著打扮，但文字介紹就相當露骨，形容佢係「高質後生靚索女」、「服務周到、天使面孔、小小蠻腰、修長美腿&hellip;&hellip;」，按摩加泰式特別服務盛惠 $488。<br />\n<br />\n　　網頁報稱「小仙女BABY」三圍34D、24、34身高162CM，同何依婷報稱164CM及參選港姐時報稱32B、22、34有出入。網頁已經有超過八千次瀏覽，Regina接受訪問時對於自己被色情網站盜用相片表示震驚，會通知公司處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2rsobik.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2rsobik.jpg&h=fd0593ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a453dbebd677d01d21df92116bce07ab03672e3b","tid":2227113,"uid":127929,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T13:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/byJEETg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbyJEETg.png&h=88b91e2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40816efaab7d426f94dc366398703e52fa8a5493","tid":2227113,"uid":81505,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a453dbebd677d01d21df92116bce07ab03672e3b","tid":2227113,"uid":127929,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T13:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/byJEETg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbyJEETg.png&h=88b91e2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T13:57:56.000Z","msg":"你班仆街又屈梁sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}